OL,3,CWhy politicians are voting over
OL,4,Cwhether to suspend a former Chief
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FIf the motion is passed, Deputy St
OL,8,FPier will be suspended from the
OL,9,FAssembly for 25 days - potentially
OL,10,Fwithout pay.
OL,12,FIt's part of a long dispute between
OL,13,Fthe politician and local paediatrician
OL,14,FDr Sandie Bohin.
OL,16,FHow did Deputy St Pier break the
OL,17,FStates' Code of Conduct?
