OL,3,CWhy politicians are voting over
OL,4,Cwhether to suspend a former Chief
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FHer investigation found that he had
OL,8,Fbreached six sections of the Deputy's
OL,9,FCode of Conduct when speaking to a
OL,10,Fjournalist from The Guardian about
OL,11,Fhealth cases relating to Dr Bohin.
OL,13,FIn response, Deputy St Pier stressed
OL,14,Fthat he only confirmed a series of
OL,15,Ffacts, and criticised the
OL,16,Frecommendation to suspend him as
OL,17,F"extraordinary and dystopian".
