OL,3,CWhy politicians are voting over
OL,4,Cwhether to suspend a former Chief
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FIt originally recommended a 30-day
OL,8,Fsuspension, which was reduced to 25
OL,9,Fdays on appeal.
OL,11,FA joint amendment from Deputies Sarah
OL,12,FHansmann Rouxel and Yvonne Burford
OL,13,Falso wants the suspension to be unpaid.
OL,15,FDeputy St Pier has defended himself
OL,16,Fthat he was advocating for several
OL,17,Ffamilies with safeguarding concerns
OL,18,Fabout Guernsey's medical sector.
OL,20,FWhat do Dr Sandie Bohin and the
OL,21,FMedical Specialist Group say?
