OL,3,CWhy politicians are voting over
OL,4,Cwhether to suspend a former Chief
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FDr Bohin welcomed the Commissioner's
OL,8,Freport calling for the suspension.
OL,10,F"(The report) is a fair, comprehensive
OL,11,Fand evidence-based investigation that
OL,12,Fconfirmed the allegations about me
OL,13,Fwere inaccurate," Dr Bohin revealed in
OL,14,Fa statement.
OL,16,F"I could not have asked for a more
OL,17,Fthorough report."
