OL,3,CWhy politicians are voting over
OL,4,Cwhether to suspend a former Chief
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FDr Steve Evans, the MSG's Chair,
OL,8,Fargues the politician caused "deep
OL,9,Fharm" to Dr Bohin, the paediatric
OL,10,Fservice and public trust by naming the
OL,11,Fdoctor.
OL,13,FThe MSG has been supported by the
OL,14,FBritish Medical Association (BMA),
OL,15,Falleging Guernsey's health sector is
OL,16,F"at risk of destabilisation" if
OL,17,Fpoliticians fail to suspend Deputy
OL,18,FGavin St Pier.
